    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a parts donor. The exterior suffers from significant rust, peeling paint, and several noticeable body dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the seats and a non-functional climate control system. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention due to a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips between gears; it is not currently suitable for reliable daily transportation.",
